<section>

<h2 class="title">Karier & Kompetensi</h2>

<div class="timeline">

<div class="timeline-item">
<h3>Radiologi Digital</h3>
<p>PACS, RIS, Modalitas Radiologi, Workflow Imaging.</p>
</div>

<div class="timeline-item">
