<p>Pengembangan dan pengelolaan sistem informasi rumah sakit.</p>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<section id="social">

<h2 class="title">Media Sosial</h2>

<div class="social-grid">

<a href="#" class="social whatsapp">WhatsApp</a>

<a href="#" class="social instagram">Instagram</a>

<a href="#" class="social facebook">Facebook</a>

<a href="#" class="social tiktok">TikTok</a>

<a href="#" class="social youtube">YouTube</a>

<a href="#" class="social linkedin">LinkedIn</a>

</div>

</section>

<section>

<div class="glass" style="text-align:center">

<h2>Hubungi Saya</h2>

<br>

<p>Email : eko@example.com</p>
<p>WhatsApp : +62 xxx xxxx xxxx</p>
<p>Instansi : RSPAD Gatot Soebroto</p>

</div>

</section>

<footer>

© 2026 Eko Risdianto • Personal Landing Page • Built With Passion

</footer>

</body>
</html>
